Scientists declare: 'Human activities are changing Earth's climate'.
Could someone explain why the fuck the whole world can't just use nuclear power?
Because there isn't an infinite amount of uranium available. If we replaced all energy production with nuclear power, we'd be out of uranium in a couple of decades.
